rows.label: tlk70000049_01_msg001
rows.name:
Though not quite as urgent as that
all-important healing herb, there are
other medicines that I regularly require.

rows.label: tlk70000049_01_msg002
rows.name:
Sleeping medications in particular are
always in high demand from a few
particular customers.

rows.label: tlk70000049_01_msg003
rows.name:
I fear some have sustained great scars
of the heart. The horrors they have
witnessed must keep them up at night.

rows.label: tlk70000049_01_msg004
rows.name:
Though others simply have trouble
sleeping because Iiran pillows are
not soft enough for their taste.

rows.label: tlk70000049_01_msg005
rows.name:
The next most requested medicine is
for health of the liver, particularly just
after new recruits have joined.

rows.label: tlk70000049_01_msg006
rows.name:
They hold contests, you see, to find out
which nation can handle their booze
the best. Inadvisable, in my opinion.
